{"tid":466330,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下個HDD 係咪就死","createTime":"2017-11-12T12:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T17:21:18.000Z","uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c77a057cff5b2f2fed568ea6eb30c13d42cd05a2","tid":466330,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:44:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k0oirf9w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk0oirf9w&h=5c1d0bc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部腦近排開機神神地，試過<br />\n開機未入到桌面就卡死；<br />\n開機入到去桌面無耐就藍Mon 死或者無藍Mon 直接卡死，仲會有噪音；<br />\n就算無卡死，用嗰陣有時仲會頓下頓下，即係郁個鼠標會瞬移咁。<br />\n想問下係咪好有可能係HDD問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係其他硬件有問題？ 唔該咁多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194e7aa7a046b9e49801a86fab0b791197186efc","tid":466330,"uid":69778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:01:33.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n其實你幅圖都答左"},{"pid":"554444fbb3097b5c78123a4477135e2c8adcc72b","tid":466330,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<br />\n其實你幅圖都答左</blockquote><br />\n其實係兩年前都係好似幅圖咁樣，但係嗰陣未有我上面字述嘅情況<br />\n會唔會有可能係其他硬件問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204aff1c30c227b6085dd4dab70283be91968df8","tid":466330,"uid":82970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9f55250e8fb40aa2c0cf9a2082df79227582ab2","tid":466330,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"有冇緊要野係入面?<br />\n有就快手BACKUP左先<br />\n冇就用到死先算"},{"pid":"4247a47cb600c2dd8e0bb6f5812032d7f0e5221e","tid":466330,"uid":14936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:48:01.